    <item>
      <title>中国誓言对金融犯罪零容忍，将重新审视处罚措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/china-vows-zero-tolerance-for-financial-crimes-will-review-punishments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国金融监管机构表示，将对违法行为采取“零容忍”态度，并将考虑修改处罚规则，以确保犯罪者付出“惨痛代价”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/china-vows-zero-tolerance-for-financial-crimes-will-review-punishments</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 09:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
