      <title>英国通胀将放缓，但速度不会像市场希望的那么快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/uk-inflation-is-set-to-ease-but-not-as-quickly-as-markets-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国的通胀压力本周将再次缓解，但速度不会像投资者所希望的那么快，因为他们押注一轮迅速降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/uk-inflation-is-set-to-ease-but-not-as-quickly-as-markets-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
