      <title>价格战导致中国消费类股暴跌 1,570 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/price-wars-help-spark-157-billion-rout-in-china-consumer-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在消费者需求不温不火的情况下，中国商品价格看似持续下跌，削弱了企业盈利能够重振低迷股市的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/price-wars-help-spark-157-billion-rout-in-china-consumer-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
