      <title>卡梅伦称全球风险仪表板上“红灯闪烁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/cameron-says-uk-ready-to-strike-houthis-if-attacks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦在媒体露面时表示，全球风险水平“呈红色闪烁”，如果胡塞武装继续袭击红海船只，英国准备对胡塞武装目标进行进一步打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/cameron-says-uk-ready-to-strike-houthis-if-attacks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 22:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024年中国的复苏将“缓慢而坎坷”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/world-economy-latest-china-s-recovery-will-be-slow-and-bumpy-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国看起来几乎肯定会实现 2023 年约 5% 的增长目标，人们的注意力转向通货紧缩风险、房地产危机和持续存在的信心紧缩是否会破坏今年建立动力的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/world-economy-latest-china-s-recovery-will-be-slow-and-bumpy-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称投票后美国不支持台独</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/biden-says-us-does-not-support-taiwan-s-independence-after-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，在台湾选民反抗中国并回归执政的民进党之后，美国不支持台湾独立。它试图限制北京的影响力——至连续第三个任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/biden-says-us-does-not-support-taiwan-s-independence-after-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 15:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
